<codeline lineno="3"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="4"><highlight class="comment">Description<sp/>of<sp/>a<sp/>web<sp/>crawler<sp/>example<sp/>in<sp/>XQuery.&lt;br/&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="5"><highlight class="comment">Entire<sp/>script<sp/>can<sp/>be<sp/>seen<sp/>here:<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="6"><highlight class="comment">\link<sp/>link_crawler2</highlight></codeline>
