<codeline lineno="22"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="23"><highlight class="comment">The<sp/>internal<sp/>pages<sp/>are<sp/>checked<sp/>recursively,<sp/>while<sp/>the<sp/>external<sp/>ones<sp/>are<sp/>only<sp/>checked<sp/>for<sp/>existence.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="24"><highlight class="comment">The<sp/>distinction<sp/>between<sp/>internal<sp/>and<sp/>external<sp/>links<sp/>is<sp/>made<sp/>by<sp/>comparing<sp/>the<sp/>URI<sp/>with<sp/>a<sp/>global<sp/>string<sp/>variable<sp/>$uri-host.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="25"><highlight class="comment">Change<sp/>this<sp/>variable<sp/>to<sp/>point<sp/>to<sp/>your<sp/>website,<sp/>or<sp/>a<sp/>subdirectory<sp/>on<sp/>your<sp/>website.</highlight></codeline>
