<codeline lineno="37"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="38"><highlight class="comment">The<sp/>crawling<sp/>starts<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>URI<sp/>pointed<sp/>by<sp/>$top-uri.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="39"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
